title: After fire and quake, now malibu's name is mud
author: Unknown
text: LARRY ABBOTT SLOGS THROUGH A RIVER OF MUCK YESTERDAY AFTER MUDSLIDES, TRIGGERED BY HEAVY RAIN, INUNDATED HIS HOME AND SEVERAL OTHERS IN MALIBU, CALIF. DETAILS, A 5.Caption:  PHOTOREED SAXON / AP: AFTER FIRE AND QUAKE, NOW MALIBU'S NAME IS MUD
